ts/toggle-button#sizes","content":"Two sizes are available: `sm` and `md` (default)."},"750":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-35","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#icon--text","content":"Items can include an `Icon` alongside text for added visual context."},"751":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-36","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#icon-only","content":"For compact layouts, items can contain only icons. Padding adjusts automatically to keep the button square — no extra prop required. Always provide an `aria-label` on each icon-only item so screen readers can identify the action."},"752":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-37","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#with-dropdown","content":"Wrap a `ToggleButton` in a `MenuTrigger` to add sub-options to a group item."},"753":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-38","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#rtl-direction","content":"The group follows the document's layout direction, detected automatically from the browser locale."},"754":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-39","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#data-attributes","content":"Components automatically add data attributes for styling different states:"},"755":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-40","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#data-attributes","content":"**ToggleButtonGroup Container:** `data-size`"},"756":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-41","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#data-attributes","content":"**ToggleButton Item:** `data-selected`, `data-hovered`